<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Shift Management – BlueLight Guardian 24/7</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Shift Management guidance for BlueLight Guardian 24/7."
  />
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#F6F9FF;
      --police-blue:#3B82F6;
      --accent-blue:#2563EB;
      --highlight:#60A5FA;
      --text:#0F172A;
      --muted:#64748B;
      --line:#E2E8F0;
      --white:#FFFFFF;
      --surface:#FFFFFF;
      --surface-soft:#F8FBFF;
      --note-bg:#EFF6FF;
      --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);
      --radius-xl:24px;
      --radius-lg:18px;
      --radius-md:12px;
      --container:1120px;
    }

    *{
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    html{
      scroll-behavior:smooth;
    }

    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
      line-height:1.7;
    }

    a{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:inherit;
    }

    img{
      max-width:100%;
      display:block;
    }

    .container{
      width:min(var(--container), calc(100% - 2rem));
      margin:0 auto;
    }

    .navbar{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:1000;
      background:rgba(246,249,255,0.92);
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
      backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    }

    .nav-inner{
      min-height:78px;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:center;
      gap:20px;
    }

    .logo{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:14px;
    }

    .logo-box{
      width:48px;
      height:48px;
      border-radius:14px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--police-blue), var(--accent-blue));
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      color:white;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:0.02em;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .logo-box img{
      width:100%;
      height:100%;
      object-fit:cover;
    }

    .logo-copy{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:2px;
    }

    .brand{
      font-size:1rem;
      font-weight:800;
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .subbrand{
      font-size:0.9rem;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .nav-links{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:22px;
    }

    .nav-links a{
      color:#334155;
      font-weight:600;
      font-size:0.95rem;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover{
      color:var(--accent-blue);
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      min-height:46px;
      padding:0 18px;
      border-radius:12px;
      border:1px solid transparent;
      font-weight:700;
      transition:0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary{
      background:var(--accent-blue);
      color:white;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover{
      background:#1D4ED8;
    }

    .btn-secondary{
      background:white;
      color:var(--accent-blue);
      border-color:var(--line);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover{
      border-color:#BFDBFE;
      background:#F8FBFF;
    }

    .hero{
      padding:56px 0 28px;
    }

    .hero-card{
      background:var(--surface);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:var(--radius-xl);
      padding:32px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .eyebrow{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:8px 14px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:#EFF6FF;
      color:var(--accent-blue);
      font-size:0.85rem;
      font-weight:700;
      border:1px solid #DBEAFE;
      margin-bottom:16px;
    }

    .hero h1{
      margin:0 0 14px;
      font-size:clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      line-height:1.05;
      letter-spacing:-0.04em;
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .hero p{
      margin:0;
      max-width:70ch;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:1.02rem;
    }

    .hero-actions{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:12px;
      margin-top:24px;
    }

    .page-layout{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:280px 1fr;
      gap:24px;
      padding:20px 0 72px;
    }

    .sidebar{
      align-self:start;
      position:sticky;
      top:100px;
      background:var(--surface);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:22px;
      box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(15,23,42,0.03);
    }

    .sidebar h3{
      margin:0 0 14px;
      font-size:1rem;
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .sidebar a{
      display:block;
      padding:10px 0;
      color:#334155;
      font-weight:600;
      font-size:0.95rem;
      border-bottom:1px solid #EEF2F7;
    }

    .sidebar a:last-child{
      border-bottom:none;
    }

    .sidebar a:hover{
      color:var(--accent-blue);
    }

    .content{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:22px;
    }

    .doc-section{
      background:var(--surface);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:28px;
      box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(15,23,42,0.03);
    }

    .doc-section h2{
      margin:0 0 14px;
      font-size:1.55rem;
      letter-spacing:-0.02em;
      color:var(--text);
    }

    .doc-section h3{
      margin:22px 0 10px;
      font-size:1.05rem;
      color:var(--accent-blue);
    }

    .doc-section p{
      margin:0 0 14px;
      color:#334155;
    }

    .doc-section ul,
    .doc-section ol{
      margin:0 0 14px 0;
      padding-left:22px;
      color:#334155;
    }

    .intro-list{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap:14px;
      margin-top:18px;
    }

    .mini-card{
      background:var(--surface-soft);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:16px;
    }

    .mini-card strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:6px;
      color:var(--text);
      font-size:0.96rem;
    }

    .mini-card span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:0.94rem;
    }

    .image-box{
      margin:18px 0 8px;
      text-align:center;
    }

    .image-box img{
      width:100%;
      max-width:760px;
      margin:0 auto;
      border-radius:16px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:#F8FAFC;
      box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(15,23,42,0.03);
    }

    .caption{
      margin-top:10px;
      font-size:0.9rem;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .table-wrap{
      overflow-x:auto;
      margin:14px 0 8px;
    }

    table{
      width:100%;
      border-collapse:collapse;
      min-width:620px;
      background:white;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:12px;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    th, td{
      padding:12px 14px;
      text-align:left;
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    }

    th{
      background:#F8FBFF;
      color:var(--text);
      font-size:0.94rem;
    }

    td{
      color:#334155;
      font-size:0.95rem;
    }

    tr:last-child td{
      border-bottom:none;
    }

    .note{
      background:var(--note-bg);
      border:1px solid #DBEAFE;
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:16px 18px;
      margin-top:14px;
      color:#1E3A8A;
    }

    .step-block{
      margin-top:14px;
      padding-top:10px;
      border-top:1px solid #EEF2F7;
    }

    .step-block:first-of-type{
      border-top:none;
      padding-top:0;
    }

    .footer{
      border-top:1px solid var(--line);
      padding:32px 0 48px;
      background:#FAFCFF;
    }

    .footer-inner{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:20px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .footer p{
      margin:0;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .footer span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px){
      .page-layout{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .sidebar{
        position:static;
      }

      .intro-list{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px){
      .nav-inner{
        flex-direction:column;
        align-items:flex-start;
        padding:14px 0;
      }

      .nav-links{
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        gap:14px;
      }

      .hero-card,
      .doc-section,
      .sidebar{
        padding:22px;
      }

      .footer-inner{
        flex-direction:column;
        align-items:flex-start;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 520px){
      .hero-actions{
        flex-direction:column;
      }

      .btn{
        width:100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="container nav-inner">
      <a href="index.html" class="logo">
        <div class="logo-box">BG</div>
        <div class="logo-copy">
          <span class="brand">BlueLight Guardian 24/7</span>
          <span class="subbrand">Emergency service wellbeing platform</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="index.html#features">Features</a>
        <a href="index.html#access">Access</a>
        <a href="index.html#download" class="btn btn-primary">Request Demo</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-card">
          <span class="eyebrow">Feature Guide</span>
          <h1>Shift Management</h1>
          <p>
            The Shift Management module enables police officers and emergency service
            personnel to plan, create and manage work schedules efficiently using
            custom shifts, shift patterns and reusable shift cycles.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="index.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Back to Homepage</a>
            <a href="#section-1-2" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Custom Shift</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container page-layout">
        <aside class="sidebar">
          <h3>On this page</h3>
          <a href="#section-overview">1. Overview</a>
          <a href="#section-1-1">1.1 Shift Schedule Creation</a>
          <a href="#section-1-2">1.2 Creating a Custom Shift</a>
          <a href="#section-1-3">1.3 Creating a Shift Pattern</a>
          <a href="#section-1-4">1.4 Shift Pattern Creation</a>
          <a href="#section-1-5">1.5 Shift Cycle Creation</a>
        </aside>

        <div class="content">
          <section class="doc-section" id="section-overview">
            <h2>1. Shift Management</h2>
            <p>
              The Shift Management module enables police officers and emergency service personnel
              to plan, create and manage their work schedules efficiently.
            </p>

            <div class="image-box">
              <img src="images/shift-dashboard.png" alt="Shift Management dashboard" />
              <p class="caption">Figure 1: Shift Management Dashboard</p>
            </div>

            <div class="intro-list">
              <div class="mini-card">
                <strong>Custom Shifts</strong>
                <span>Create individual shifts for specific dates.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mini-card">
                <strong>Shift Patterns</strong>
                <span>Generate repeating schedules using reusable cycles.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mini-card">
                <strong>Schedule Views</strong>
                <span>Review shifts in both list and calendar view.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mini-card">
                <strong>Flexible Editing</strong>
                <span>Modify or reuse existing patterns and cycles.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="doc-section" id="section-1-1">
            <h2>1.1 Shift Schedule Creation</h2>
            <p>
              Users can create schedules using the <strong>Create Shift</strong> option.
            </p>

            <div class="image-box">
              <img src="images/create-shift-menu.png" alt="Create Shift options menu" />
              <p class="caption">Figure 2: Create Shift Options Menu</p>
            </div>

            <p>Users can choose between:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Custom Shift</strong> – Create individual shifts manually.</li>
              <li><strong>Shift Pattern</strong> – Generate repeating schedules using cycles.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="doc-section" id="section-1-2">
            <h2>1.2 Creating a Custom Shift</h2>

            <div class="step-block">
              <h3>Step 1: Access Custom Shift</h3>
              <ol>
                <li>Navigate to the Shift Management screen.</li>
                <li>Tap <strong>Create Shift</strong>.</li>
                <li>Select <strong>Custom Shift</strong>.</li>
              </ol>

              <div class="image-box">
                <img src="images/custom-shift-form.png" alt="Custom Shift creation form" />
                <p class="caption">Figure 3: Custom Shift Creation Form</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step-block">
              <h3>Step 2: Enter Shift Details</h3>
              <div class="table-wrap">
                <table>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Field</th>
                    <th>Description</th>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>Date</td>
                    <td>Select the shift date</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>Shift Type</td>
                    <td>Day, Early, Night etc.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>Working Hours</td>
                    <td>Enter start and end time</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>Break Time</td>
                    <td>Optional rest period</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>Colour Code</td>
                    <td>Colour used for calendar display</td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step-block">
              <h3>Step 3: Submit and Confirm</h3>
              <ol>
                <li>Tap <strong>Submit</strong>.</li>
                <li>Review the confirmation screen.</li>
                <li>Tap <strong>Confirm</strong> to save the shift.</li>
              </ol>

              <div class="image-box">
                <img src="images/shift-confirmation.png" alt="Shift confirmation screen" />
                <p class="caption">Figure 4: Shift Confirmation Screen</p>
              </div>

              <div class="note">
                The shift will appear in:
                <ul>
                  <li>Shift Schedule List</li>
                  <li>Calendar View</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="doc-section" id="section-1-3">
            <h2>1.3 Creating a Shift Pattern</h2>
            <p>
              Shift patterns allow users to automatically generate repeating schedules
              using Shift Cycles.
            </p>

            <div class="image-box">
              <img src="images/shift-pattern-builder.png" alt="Shift Pattern Builder" />
              <p class="caption">Figure 5: Shift Pattern Builder</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step-block">
              <h3>Step 1: Create a Shift Cycle</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Enter a cycle name.</li>
                <li>Add shift entries.</li>
              </ul>

              <div class="table-wrap">
                <table>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Shift Type</th>
                    <th>Working Hours</th>
                    <th>Break</th>
                    <th>Duration</th>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td>Day Shift</td>
                    <td>09:00 – 17:00</td>
                    <td>1 hour</td>
                    <td>3 days</td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>

              <div class="note">
                <strong>Important:</strong> Every shift cycle must include at least one
                <strong>Rest Day</strong>.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step-block">
              <h3>Step 2: Add Cycle to Pattern</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Specify the number of repetitions.</li>
                <li>Add additional cycles if needed.</li>
              </ul>

              <div class="image-box">
                <img src="images/pattern-cycle-add.png" alt="Adding cycles to pattern" />
                <p class="caption">Figure 6: Adding Cycles to Pattern</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step-block">
              <h3>Step 3: Generate Schedule</h3>
              <p>Users must provide:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Start Date</li>
                <li>Number of Occurrences</li>
              </ul>
              <p>The system then automatically generates the full shift schedule.</p>

              <div class="image-box">
                <img src="images/calendar-view.png" alt="Calendar view of generated shifts" />
                <p class="caption">Figure 7: Calendar View of Generated Shifts</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="doc-section" id="section-1-4">
            <h2>1.4 Shift Pattern Creation</h2>
            <p>Users can create patterns in two ways:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Create a Custom Pattern</li>
              <li>Use an Existing Pattern</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="image-box">
              <img src="images/pattern-selection.png" alt="Pattern selection screen" />
              <p class="caption">Figure 8: Pattern Selection Screen</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="doc-section" id="section-1-5">
            <h2>1.5 Shift Cycle Creation</h2>
            <p>
              A Shift Cycle represents a repeating sequence of shifts and rest days.
            </p>

            <div class="image-box">
              <img src="images/cycle-creation.png" alt="Shift cycle creation screen" />
              <p class="caption">Figure 9: Shift Cycle Creation Screen</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <div>
        <p>BlueLight Guardian 24/7</p>
        <span>Supporting operational readiness through wellbeing-aware design.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
